---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Downtown Dry - Your Guide to Alcohol-Free Nightlife" description="Learn about Downtown Dry's mission to connect people with alcohol-free entertainment, kava bars, CBD lounges, and alternative social venues across US cities.">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-700 via-secondary-500 to-accent-500 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">ABOUT DOWNTOWN DRY</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-100 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        We're revolutionizing nightlife by connecting people with amazing alcohol-free venues and experiences across America. 
        Because great social experiences don't require alcohol.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">OUR MISSION</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Downtown Dry was founded on the belief that meaningful social experiences shouldn't revolve around alcohol consumption. We're building the most comprehensive directory of alternative venues, kava bars, CBD lounges, and alcohol-free entertainment across US cities.
            </p>
            <p>
              Whether you're exploring mindful living, in recovery, taking a break from drinking, pregnant, or simply prefer alcohol-free options, we help you discover amazing venues where you can socialize, relax, and have fun without compromise.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our platform celebrates the growing movement of people choosing wellness-focused nightlife experiences that prioritize genuine connection, mental clarity, and holistic well-being over traditional drinking culture.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-primary-700 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-xl">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold">500+</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2 font-medium">Venues Listed</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-secondary-500 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-xl">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold">50+</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2 font-medium">Cities Covered</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-accent-500 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-xl">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold">Growing</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-2 font-medium">Daily</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184291/pexels-photo-3184291.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="People socializing at alcohol-free venue" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Problem We're Solving -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">THE PROBLEM WE'RE SOLVING</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Traditional nightlife has been dominated by alcohol-centric venues, leaving many people without suitable social options
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">LIMITED OPTIONS</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Most cities lack comprehensive directories of alcohol-free social venues, making it difficult for people to find suitable nightlife alternatives.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 3a1 1 0 000 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h2.586l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 15.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L12.414 15H15a2 2 0 002-2V5a1 1 0 100-2H3zm11 4a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 102 0V7z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">SOCIAL PRESSURE</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Many people feel excluded from traditional nightlife due to alcohol-centric culture, creating a need for inclusive social spaces.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">HEALTH AWARENESS</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Growing awareness of alcohol's health impacts drives demand for venues offering natural alternatives like kava, CBD, and wellness-focused experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What We Cover -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">WHAT WE COVER</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          We specialize in venues and experiences that offer alternatives to traditional alcohol-focused nightlife
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-700 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zM3 10a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM14 9a1 1 0 00-1 1v6a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-6a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">KAVA BARS</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Traditional Pacific Island beverages in relaxed social settings perfect for unwinding after work and connecting with community.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 4a4 4 0 100 8 4 4 0 000-8zM2 8a6 6 0 1110.89 3.476l4.817 4.817a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414l-4.816-4.816A6 6 0 012 8z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">CBD LOUNGES</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Wellness-focused venues offering CBD-infused beverages and relaxation experiences for stress relief and mindful socializing.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 6a3 3 0 013-3h10a1 1 0 01.8 1.6L14.25 8l2.55 3.4A1 1 0 0116 13H6a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 11-2 0V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">CANNABIS CAFES</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Legal cannabis consumption lounges in permitted states, offering safe, regulated environments for therapeutic and recreational use.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M5 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5zM5 11a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2v-2a2 2 0 00-2-2H5zM11 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zM11 13a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">MOCKTAIL BARS</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Sophisticated alcohol-free cocktail lounges with creative non-alcoholic beverages and upscale ambiance.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9 2a1 1 0 000 2h2a1 1 0 100-2H9z"/>
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 5a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zm3 1a1 1 0 000 2h.01a1 1 0 100-2H7zm3 0a1 1 0 000 2h3a1 1 0 100-2h-3zm-3 4a1 1 0 100 2h.01a1 1 0 100-2H7zm3 0a1 1 0 100 2h3a1 1 0 100-2h-3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">COFFEE & TEA LOUNGES</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Late-night coffee shops and specialty tea houses for evening socializing, perfect for dates and casual meetups.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">SOCIAL CLUBS</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Community spaces focused on connection and activities without substances as the centerpiece, featuring games, music, and conversation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Team/Contact CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">JOIN THE MOVEMENT</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Help us build the most comprehensive directory of alcohol-free venues. Whether you're a venue owner, community member, or just passionate about alternative nightlife, we'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="group bg-primary-700 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary-800 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl">
          GET IN TOUCH
          <svg class="inline-block ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="group border-2 border-primary-700 text-primary-700 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary-700 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          READ OUR BLOG
          <svg class="inline-block ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>